title: Real Humans S1 Ep8
description:
Real Humans S1 Ep8

Make Haste - In a parallel present day, robots have become so human it is barely possible to distinguish them from real people. In this episode, Rick and Bo are insulted when the ladies switch them off for a girls' night out. They begin throwing their weight about and decide to get revenge. When Inger questions Leo, he lets her know that time is running out. Meanwhile, at Roger's house, Bea begins to develop feelings and soon has a revelation for Roger. Stars Andreas Wilson, Lisette Pagler and Pia Halvorsen. 

From Sweden, in Swedish

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
